headline.main: Barty Sets Up Malaysian Open Final Against Hibino
headline.print_headline: Barty Sets Up Malaysian Open Final Against Hibino

lead_paragraph: Ashleigh Barty advanced to her first WTA singles final after beating China's Han Xinyun 6-3, 7-5 Saturday at the Malaysian Open.
